--------IDEATION TRACKER--------
class board:
stores the board (a two d array)
private cell[][] board; // cell isn't neccessary (in theory we could just use bools, but wheres the fun)
pub void display(){}; //Prints the board
pub void update(){}; // Updates the board (1 cycle)

class cell:
private bool alive; // tracks the status of the individual cell
public void update(){}; // flips the state of the cell
